title: Home Movies complete series with dvd extras and OST
description:
Home Movies complete series with dvd bonus materials and bonus OST. I've included pretty much all the dvd extras except the choose your own adventure mini games that required the dvd menu interactivity functions. Season 1 files are much larger because the squiggle vision really messed with the compression. The interviews may have high pitched background noises, they are present on the dvds as well, just more pronounced after audio compression.

If you have difficulties playing back the files using the latest VLC player usually works, or if you're more technically inclined you can try to install/fiddle with the codecs following this guide http://www.projectharuhi.net/?p=11611


Video: 656x480 h264 10bit
Audio: AAC
